'''CECIM''' - ''Centro de Educación y Capacitación Integral Hna. Maura Clarke'' (''The Center for Education and Training in Honor of Sister [[Maura Clarke]]'') is an education center located in [[Ciudad Sandino]], [[Nicaragua]].

The education center has many projects to educate the people of Ciudad Sandino, both children and adults. Cecim gives classes in e.g. sewing, baking, dancing, and thanks to money from a project in [[Sweden]] CECIM now offers acting classes.

For many years CECIM has had contact with the Swedish "[[Gymnasium (school)|gymnasium]]" ''[[Angered]]sgymnasiet'' in [[Göteborg]], [[Sweden]]. In different [[Student exchange program|exchange program]]s, students from Angeredsgymnasiet have visited CECIM, and students from CECIM has visited Angeredsgymnasiet.

